# Agentic Issue Lifecycle (mandatory)

Before implementing **any** GitHub issue from the TensorGate board:

1. Read and follow the project skill: `.cursor/skills/niw-project-lifecycle/SKILL.md`
2. Use `./scripts/project-board-transition.sh <issue#> "<Status>"` for every phase change
3. Assign `@syed-dawood` when work starts; keep audit trail on issue + PR (no "role playing" labels in text)

Order: **Todo → In Progress → Peer Review → Ready For QA → QA Complete → Done**

On review or QA failure, move the board **backward** and document on the PR.

Do not skip research comments or testing evidence on the PR body.
